課程教材 Course Material
	    (1) 生醫系統基礎 (Biomedical System Fundamentals)
(2) 電磁熱治療與生物電磁學 (Electromagnetic Thermal Therapy & Biological Electromagnetism)
(3) 奈米生醫整合系統 (Nano-Biomedical Integrated System)
(4) 手機醫療系統 (Mobile Phone-Based Medical System)
(5) 超導醫療系統 (Superconductor Medical System)
(6) 磁浮內視鏡 (MAGLEV Endoscope)
(7) 超音波生醫檢測系統 (Ultrasonic Medical Inspection System)
(8) 先進醫療系統：電腦斷層掃瞄(Computed Tomography, CT)、核磁共振影像(Magnetic Resonance Imaging, MRI)、單光子放射斷層圖(Single Photon Emission Tomography, SPECT)、正子放射斷層圖(Positron Emission Tomography , PET)
(9) 醫療器材法規(FDA)與設計管制基礎(ISO13485)
(10) 生醫工程創投 (Biomedical Engineering    

參考書目 References
	    1. “MRI the Basics”, Ray H. Hashemi, Lippincott Williams & Wilkins
2. “Adaptive Phased Array Thermotherapy for Cancer”, Alen J. Fenn, Artech House (2009)
3. “Biomedical Engineering Entrepreneurship”, Jen-Shih Lee, World Scientific (2010)
4. “Design and Development of Medical Electronic Instrumentation”, David Prutchi and Michael Norris, Wiley, 2005
5. “Introduction to Biomedical Equipment Technology”, Joseph J. Carr & J. M. Brown
6. “Medical Instrumentation – Application and Design”, John G. Webster, 4th, Wiley 2010
7. “Body Sensor Networks”, Guang-Zhong Yang (2006) Springer (亞勃克代理)
8. “Handbook of Biosensors & Electronic Noises: Medicine, Food, and the Environment”, Erika Kress-Rogers (1997), CRC Press
9. “Signals and Systems in Biomedical Engineering”, Suresh R. Devasahayam (2000), Kluwer
10. 「手機平臺上的生物醫學工程學—原理與應用」、劉靜等(大陸 科學出版社 2011)
11. 「生物電磁特性及其應用」、宋濤等 (大陸 北京工業大學出版社)
12. 「生物電磁學」、龐小峰 (大陸 國防工業出版社 2008)
13. 「生物醫學工程導論」，中華民國生物醫學工程學會 (滄海)
14. 「物理因子治療學：電磁療學」，廖文炫等 (合計圖書 2003)    

